listitem.para:
Dependency. Add a dependency between two artifacts selected using button 1 motion (from the dependent artifact). There are also 2 special types of dependency offered here, Permission (
) and Usage (
). A Permission is created by default with stereotype Import, and is used to import elements from one package into another.

